name: Alien Jump (Overloading fun)
description:
The game title is Alien Jump. Alien jump is a hyper-casual game in which you have a vertical world to go. You have to reach the end of the vertical world by jumping on different platforms and avoiding obstacles. But make sure to collect coins because coins are your score. The more the coins, the more the score. There are some points where you have to think before jumping, Thus making it a strategic game at some points. Also, you have to reach the end of this game in only 5 Minutes. So, You have to hurry but also needs to stay alert at the same time. 

Note : Please consider putting it on Fullscreen first before clicking on game to avoid no controls Problem.
